    oc:hasCategory "marketing" ;
    oc:hasDescription "When the user wants to plan, design, or implement an A/B test or experiment. Also use when the user mentions \"A/B test,\" \"split test,\" \"experiment,\" \"test this change,\" \"variant copy,\" \"multivariate test,\" \"hypothesis,\" \"should I test this,\" \"which version is better,\" \"test two versions,\" \"statistical significance,\" or \"how long should I run this test.\" Use this whenever someone is comparing two approaches and wants to measure which performs better. For tracking implementation, see analytics-tracking. For page-level conversion optimization, see page-cro." ;
